    "P3 additive interaction closure artifact-set validator checks envelope provenance, upstream hash shape, payload shapes and row types, canonical graph closure, duplicate split records, split artifact drift, message coverage, reaction applicability maps, source hash handoff provenance, and closure handoff blockers.",
